## Stack

- **Scala** 3 / **sbt**
- **ZIO 2** — effects, streams, scheduling
- **ZIO HTTP** — HTTP server
- **ZIO Config** (Typesafe/HOCON backend) — configuration
- **ZIO Logging** + **Logback** — structured logging
- **sbt-native-packager** — universal zip + Docker image
- **Docker** — published to `ghcr.io/{{ github_username }}/{{ project_name }}`

## Prerequisites

- [mise](https://mise.jdx.dev/) (manages Java and sbt versions)
- [Docker](https://docs.docker.com/get-docker/)

```bash
mise install   # installs Java 21 and sbt from .mise.toml
```

## Development

```bash
make build     # compile
make test      # run tests
make run       # run locally (reads src/main/resources/application.conf)
make format    # scalafmt
```

## Configuration

Configuration is read from `application.conf` (HOCON). Override any field with an environment variable:

| Key | Env override | Default |
|-----|-------------|---------|
| `{{ project_slug }}.name` | `APP_NAME` | `{{ class_name }}` |
| `{{ project_slug }}.port` | `HTTP_PORT` | `8080` |

## Docker

```bash
make docker    # builds image and loads it locally
# or push to ghcr.io:
sbt Docker/publish
```

## GitHub Actions

| Workflow | Trigger |
|---------|---------|
| `sbt-test-on-pull-request` | Every PR open/sync/reopen |
| `sbt-publish-on-push-to-main` | Push to `main` affecting Scala/sbt files |
